<br>
And as for EXP groups, well you are going to have people that are super picky and will sit forming a group for 2 hours until they get the absolut best combination of people, and you are also going to have the people that just want to get the first people together that will work and go at it for fun.  It's up to you what type of people you want to associate with.<br>
